{"id": "1278652199559368728", "channel_id": "1278075617228623872", "type": 19, "author_id": "1045141709580927067", "author_name": "luoqixikiss", "author_bot": false, "content": "这战斗之间的差距大小都不敢想，运气好多触发一次死扛，多开一次大招，这几乎会让你的结算伤害分数多将近50%，甚至更高，特别是尤乌，毒队之类的", "timestamp": "2024-08-29T09:47:20.584000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["593627944979660800"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1278599254188753050", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1278075617228623872", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "你遊核心玩法本質上是一種玩家們自發的玩家競賽（含大量個人觀點）", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1174180524034637854"]}
