{"id": "1278831553895464973", "channel_id": "1278075617228623872", "type": 0, "author_id": "372020544494764043", "author_name": "ariate", "author_bot": false, "content": "說到肉鴿，前期造物是比較有影響，後期有沒有都沒甚麼差距了。但重點是沒有讓人感到疊起來的感覺。黑印大多時候都去買覺醒比較實際，正常情況剩下的也只是夠買兩至三件裝。", "timestamp": "2024-08-29T21:40:01.990000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1278075617228623872", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "你遊核心玩法本質上是一種玩家們自發的玩家競賽（含大量個人觀點）", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1174180524034637854"]}
{"id": "1278831877226237955", "channel_id": "1278075617228623872", "type": 0, "author_id": "372020544494764043", "author_name": "ariate", "author_bot": false, "content": "造物和造物之間的連動很難感受到，使到隨機起來好像也只是隨機罷了，沒到影響戰局", "timestamp": "2024-08-29T21:41:19.078000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1278075617228623872", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "你遊核心玩法本質上是一種玩家們自發的玩家競賽（含大量個人觀點）", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1174180524034637854"]}
{"id": "1278832672424329226", "channel_id": "1278075617228623872", "type": 0, "author_id": "372020544494764043", "author_name": "ariate", "author_bot": false, "content": "然後一局太長了，但打起來局局感覺也是差不多，只要隊伍不是被王剋就可以了。等機制更新", "timestamp": "2024-08-29T21:44:28.668000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-08-29T21:47:41.467000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1278075617228623872", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "你遊核心玩法本質上是一種玩家們自發的玩家競賽（含大量個人觀點）", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1174180524034637854"]}
{"id": "1278833939733020819", "channel_id": "1278075617228623872", "type": 0, "author_id": "372020544494764043", "author_name": "ariate", "author_bot": false, "content": "還有一點比較致命是，你過不了的關卡一般和練度有關，你肉鴿的策略影響有限", "timestamp": "2024-08-29T21:49:30.818000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1278075617228623872", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "你遊核心玩法本質上是一種玩家們自發的玩家競賽（含大量個人觀點）", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1174180524034637854"]}
